OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThere will still be a lot of
OL,6,Fcloud around on Saturday with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of mostly light and patchy
OL,8,Fdrizzle developing, and transferring
OL,9,Fnorthwards during the day. Feeling a
OL,10,Flittle milder.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy overnight
OL,13,Fwith further outbreaks of light
OL,14,Fdrizzle, however some heavier bursts
OL,15,Fare possible in the west during the
OL,16,Fsecond half of the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
